g.title: j1126362286
g.text: Do you mind if I pick your brain?

g.title: j2545295116
g.text: Not literally, ha ha.

g.title: j3964834701
g.text: Imagine, me scraping bits of jelly out of your trepanned skull!

g.title: j2328108510
g.text: Honestly, I'm curious about you. Where you come from, what you've lived through.

g.title: j2487384659
g.text: I saw some, as you know, and I'd love to see more. But only if you're willing.

g.title: j3255229564
g.text: Why not.

g.title: j3395376910
g.text: So you're asking permission now?

g.title: j3406831729
g.text: No thanks. [End.]

g.title: j3261243458
g.text: OK. Where do you want to start?

g.title: j1077086756
g.text: Last time I probed you, you were freshly puked out of an Infested nightmare.

g.title: j3132706642
g.text: Suit yourself.

g.title: j1476330141
g.text: WELL.

g.title: j1191250876
g.text: I had to place the security of the Hex above courtesy.

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j3254086665
g.text: Letâ€™s say you felt like taking me on a whistle-stop tour of your favourite memories. Where would YOU start?

g.title: j3345700316
g.text: If that's a dealbreaker for you, I understand.

g.title: j3673593804
g.text: Duviri.

g.title: j2276857808
g.text: The Origin System.

g.title: j2614873915
g.text: The Entrati Family.

g.title: j1878737720
g.text: The Lotus.

g.title: j3649977313
g.text: My best ever bathroom experience. [End.]

g.title: j909354120
g.text: No mind probes. [End.]

g.title: j1319656392
g.text: It's a kingdom I used to rule.

g.title: j2992687161
g.text: You've barely made it to Lua. In my time, we have colonies on all the planets.

g.title: j3173113791
g.text: The rest of the clan are... pretty unique. And infested.

g.title: j2749029631
g.text: She's kind of a mother figure. Also kind of a biological-mechanical-deity-thing.

g.title: j26918197
g.text: Oh for Sol's sake, grow up.

g.title: j4267014067
g.text: I love how you just throw that out so casually.

g.title: j904847404
g.text: Well, excuse us for being slow off the mark.

g.title: j2143605335
g.text: Entrati has a family?

g.title: j1820914220
g.text: Oh, you are speaking my language extremely fluently.

g.title: j3816302003
g.text: "Oh, just a kingdom, I have loads."

g.title: j1444483617
g.text: Though... we aren't taking the best care of this place.

g.title: j1307653377
g.text: Entrati's had SEX?

g.title: j2318657276
g.text: Who is she to YOU, though?

g.title: j1008545504
g.text: Hmmm. I'm not sure I'll like you if you turn out to be royalty.

g.title: j48251020
g.text: The thought of what mankind could have done to other worlds makes me queasy.

g.title: j3983203320
g.text: I genuinely cannot imagine what sort of ghoulish gallery might be in store here.

g.title: j1602340305
g.text: And why is she a 'The' and not a 'Mrs' or a 'Queen' or whatnot?

g.title: j3917175706
g.text: Mind if I step inside your mind and take a look?

g.title: j1687481265
g.text: Mind if I step inside your mind and take a look?

g.title: j853490234
g.text: This is... *astonishing*

g.title: j2417567184
g.text: ... there's a future. We make it. As a species.

g.title: j456131638
g.text: They're so... human. So petty. Like bickering Gods.

g.title: j434317458
g.text: Oh. Oh my.

g.title: j2018411376
g.text: It's a living metaphor and a fabulous wish-fulfilment paradise AND sheer hell

g.title: j3858970364
g.text: I'm sorry, that must seem so obvious to you. But to me...

g.title: j1760725685
g.text: And so very much themselves, even though they're... what was the word? Wormed. Through and through.

g.title: j11825951
g.text: Natah, Margulis, Lotus. Three queens in darkness.

g.title: j177423784
g.text: You did not mention the endless executions bit. For all you know, I might have LIKED the endless executions bit.

g.title: j2804239450
g.text: So many times I've been convinced we were just going to fizzle out on this rock

g.title: j546019789
g.text: I can't pretend I understand Entrati any better after seeing this lot.

g.title: j3062120991
g.text: I just want to sit at her knee and listen to her talk.

g.title: j2178228997
g.text: ... I'm going to need to step away and process this. Dear Sol in heaven.

g.title: j4167492874
g.text: But we don't. We carry on. Thank you for showing me that.

g.title: j2016276721
g.text: But it's a comfort to know that whatever else may have changed in your time, families are still at one another's throats.

g.title: j3698850425
g.text: And now I'm torn between being grateful that you've shown her to me and murderously jealous that you get to be her Champion and I don't.
